PRIVACY POLICY
for Easy Big Text
Last updated: January 25, 2026
1. Introduction
Thank you for using Easy Big Text.
We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains how information is handled when you use our mobile application.
By using the application, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
2. Information We Collect
We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal data.
All text, files, and settings created or imported by the user remain entirely on the device and are never uploaded to external servers.
3. Data Storage and Processing
All data is processed locally on your device.
We do not operate any external servers for storing user data.
We do not use cloud storage for user-generated content.
4. Third Party Services
Our application may use third-party services that collect limited technical information for the purpose of analytics, performance monitoring, and crash reporting.
These services may collect anonymized technical data such as:
Device model
Operating system version
Application version
Crash logs
Anonymous usage statistics
This information is used solely to improve application performance and stability.
Third-party service providers are required to comply with applicable data protection regulations.
5. Advertising
Easy Big Text does not display third-party advertisements.
We do not share any data with advertisers.
6. In-App Purchases
All payments are processed securely through Apple App Store.
We do not collect or store any payment or billing information.
7. Children's Privacy
Our application does not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13.
If you believe that a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us and we will immediately delete such information.
8. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information.
Since no personal data is collected or stored on our servers, the risk of unauthorized access is minimized.
9. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
Any changes will be published on this page with an updated revision date.
10. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:
Email: neo321654@rambler.ru
